<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cheat-v">cheat <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tʃiːt/    美 /tʃiːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>欺骗；蒙骗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People making friends online are afraid of getting cheated.
网上交友的人害怕被骗。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>cheat sb (out) of</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He cheated the old woman out of her money. 
他骗了老太太的钱。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(尤指在竞赛、游戏或考试中) 作弊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is wrong to cheat in examinations.
考试作弊是不对的。</p></div></div>